                    "text": "<i>greataxe</i> +16 [<a aonid=\"322\" game-obj=\"Rules\"><u>+11/+6</u></a>] (<a aonid=\"103\" game-obj=\"Traits\"><u>magical</u></a>, <a aonid=\"194\" game-obj=\"Traits\"><u>sweep</u></a>), <b>Damage</b> 1d12+9 slashing",
